editorialNotes.standard: With this AI-powered app, musicians can perfect their performances. By isolating individual instruments in pretty much any recording, Moises helps you focus on singing lead vocals, unleashing that guitar solo, or playing bass alongside your favorite band.

You don’t need to know a lick of music theory to crank out seriously impressive tunes with Medly. This impressive sequencer lets you create deeply customisable songs with simple gestures: draw a line to add notes, tap to delete, pinch to see the whole track, and more. A variety of instruments help transform each sound, while modifiable mixers and effects ensure limitless ways to fine-tune your creations.
editorialNotes.short: Compose awesome tunes using simple gestures.
